  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    This example demonstrates the use of Spatial Anchors:
    https://developers.snap.com/spectacles/about-spectacles-features/apis/spatial-anchors
    
    Start the Lens and create a new area. Slowly scan your surroundings—this works best in smaller spaces, such as a desk area.
    
    Once the area is set up, enter it and begin placing widgets around you.
    
    The next time you re-enter the same area, the widgets should appear in the same locations.
    
    Optionally, the Cloud Storage module allows you to save anchor data to the cloud, so the experience remains consistent across different devices.he results will be the same 
